text: Bartosz Sroga (born 25 May 1976) is a Polish rower. He competed in the men's coxed pair event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1976 births Category:Living people Category:Polish male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Poland Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Gdańsk
